high_descs: Turn around to your right then face the shelf
Pick up the credit card on the shelf
Turn right then move forward, turn left head to the sofa on your right
Put the credit card on the box at the sofa
Pick up the box from the sofa
Turn left walk straight then turn left, then face the table on your left
Put the box with credit card on the right side of the table
anns.task_desc: Put the box with credit card on the right side of the table

high_descs: Turn right and walk towards the wall, then turn right and walk up to the black bench.
Pick up the blue credit card off of the bench.
Turn right and walk forward, then hang a right and walk towards the door, hang a left and walk over to the black couch with the cardboard box on its seat.
Put the blue credit card in the cardboard box that is on the couch.
Pick up the cardboard box with the credit card in it.
Walk around to the far side of the coffee table.
Put the cardboard box with the credit card in it on the right side of the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Put a cardboard box with a credit card in it on the coffee table.

high_descs: Turn and go to the table by the wall.
Pick up the credit card on the table.
Turn around and go to the sofa.
Put the credit card in the box on the sofa.
Pick up the box on the sofa..
Turn and go to the coffee table.
Put the box on the coffee table.
anns.task_desc: Move a box from the sofa to the coffee table.
